{"openapi":"3.1.0","info":{"title":"MeetMinutes","description":"This is a MeetMinutes apis documentation page","version":"3.10.0"},"paths":{"/payment/stripe/webhook":{"post":{"tags":["payment","stripe"],"summary":"Webhook Received","description":"Main Stripe webhook endpoint.\n\nAlways returns HTTP 200 once the request body is received — Stripe only\nneeds acknowledgement that the event was delivered. Internal handler\nerrors and unhandled event types are surfaced in the response body, not\nvia HTTP status, so Stripe does not retry and trigger delivery-failure\nemail notifications.","operationId":"webhook_received_payment_stripe_webhook_post","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}},"404":{"description":"Not found"}}}},"/payment/razorpay/webhook":{"post":{"tags":["payment","razorpay"],"summary":"Razorpay Webhook","description":"FastAPI endpoint that receives all Razorpay webhook events.\n\nConfigure this URL in Razorpay Dashboard → Settings → Webhooks:\n    https://<your-domain>/razorpay/webhook\n\nAlways returns HTTP 200 once the request body is received — Razorpay only\nneeds acknowledgement that the event was delivered. Internal handler\nerrors, unhandled event types, and duplicate events are surfaced in the\nresponse body, not via HTTP status, so Razorpay does not retry and\ntrigger delivery-failure email notifications.","operationId":"razorpay_webhook_payment_razorpay_webhook_post","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}},"404":{"description":"Not found"}}}},"/payment/stripe-payment-links/create-payment-link":{"post":{"tags":["payment","Stripe Payments"],"summary":"Create Payment Link or Checkout Session for Any Plan","description":"Universal endpoint that creates either a Checkout Session or Payment Link.\n\n**Smart Selection Logic:**\n- **With `customer_email`** → Checkout Session (personalized, supports cancel_url)\n- **Without `customer_email`** → Payment Link (reusable, shareable URL)\n\n**Rich Metadata Strategy:**\nAll plan details are embedded as metadata on every Stripe object so the\nwebhook handler can extract the full plan context without any database lookup.\n\n**Available Plans (all prices in USD, adaptive pricing enabled):**\n\n*Starter English (EN) — $7.99/mo, $72.00/yr:*\nstarter_en_monthly_fixed, starter_en_monthly_subscription, starter_en_monthly_subscription_no_trial,\nstarter_en_yearly_fixed, starter_en_yearly_subscription, starter_en_yearly_subscription_no_trial\n\n*Starter Multilingual (ML) — $7.99/mo, $72.00/yr:*\nstarter_ml_monthly_fixed, starter_ml_monthly_subscription, starter_ml_monthly_subscription_no_trial,\nstarter_ml_yearly_fixed, starter_ml_yearly_subscription, starter_ml_yearly_subscription_no_trial\n\n*Pro English (EN) — $21.99/mo, $168.00/yr:*\npro_en_monthly_fixed, pro_en_monthly_subscription, pro_en_monthly_subscription_no_trial,\npro_en_yearly_fixed, pro_en_yearly_subscription, pro_en_yearly_subscription_no_trial\n\n*Pro Multilingual (ML) — $21.99/mo, $168.00/yr:*\npro_ml_monthly_fixed, pro_ml_monthly_subscription, pro_ml_monthly_subscription_no_trial,\npro_ml_yearly_fixed, pro_ml_yearly_subscription, pro_ml_yearly_subscription_no_trial\n\n*Business English (EN) — $43.49/mo, $408.00/yr:*\nbusiness_v2_en_monthly_fixed, business_v2_en_monthly_subscription, business_v2_en_monthly_subscription_no_trial,\nbusiness_v2_en_yearly_fixed, business_v2_en_yearly_subscription, business_v2_en_yearly_subscription_no_trial\n\n*Business Multilingual (ML) — $43.49/mo, $408.00/yr:*\nbusiness_v2_ml_monthly_fixed, business_v2_ml_monthly_subscription, business_v2_ml_monthly_subscription_no_trial,\nbusiness_v2_ml_yearly_fixed, business_v2_ml_yearly_subscription, business_v2_ml_yearly_subscription_no_trial\n\n*Enterprise V2 (custom INR pricing):*\nenterprise_v2_monthly_subscription, enterprise_v2_yearly_subscription\n\n*Credit Packs (one-time):*\ncredit_pack_english_200 ($2.40), credit_pack_english_500 ($5.41),\ncredit_pack_multilingual_200 ($4.20), credit_pack_multilingual_500 ($9.63)","operationId":"create_payment_link_payment_stripe_payment_links_create_payment_link_post","requestBody":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/CreatePaymentLinkRequest"}}},"required":true},"responses":{"201":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/PaymentLinkResponse"}}}},"404":{"description":"Plan Not Found"},"400":{"description":"Bad Request"},"500":{"description":"Internal Server Error"},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/payment/razorpay/plans/create-payment-link":{"post":{"tags":["payment","Plan-Based Payments"],"summary":"Create Payment Link from Plan Name","description":"Create a payment link or subscription based on plan configuration.\n\n**How it works:**\n1. Accepts a plan name (e.g., ``productivity_pro_monthly_subscription``)\n2. Loads plan configuration automatically\n3. Determines billing type from the plan name:\n   - Names containing ``_subscription`` → recurring subscription\n   - All other names (``_fixed``, ``enterprise_fixed``) → one-time payment link\n4. Creates the appropriate Razorpay entity with enriched ``notes`` so\n   webhook handlers can identify the plan without secondary lookups.\n\n**Notes / Webhook Context:**\n\nEvery entity embeds full plan metadata in ``notes``::\n\n    {\n      \"plan_name\":         \"business_monthly_subscription\",\n      \"plan_tier\":         \"Business\",\n      \"usage_cycle\":       \"fixed_monthly\",\n      \"billing_cycle\":     \"monthly\",\n      \"billing_period\":    \"monthly\",\n      \"plan_display_name\": \"Business - Monthly Subscription\",\n      \"amount\":            \"299900\",\n      \"currency\":          \"INR\",\n      \"trial_enabled\":     \"True\",\n      \"trial_days\":        \"7\"\n    }\n\nUse ``RazorpayPaymentHandler.extract_plan_context_from_notes(entity[\"notes\"])``\nin webhook handlers to obtain properly typed values.\n\n**Supported Plans:**\n\n*Productivity Pro:*\nproductivity_pro_monthly_fixed, productivity_pro_yearly_fixed,\nproductivity_pro_monthly_subscription, productivity_pro_monthly_subscription_no_trial,\nproductivity_pro_yearly_subscription, productivity_pro_yearly_subscription_no_trial\n\n*Business:*\nbusiness_monthly_fixed, business_yearly_fixed,\nbusiness_monthly_subscription, business_monthly_subscription_no_trial,\nbusiness_yearly_subscription, business_yearly_subscription_no_trial\n\n*Enterprise:*\nenterprise_fixed (one-time lifetime deal only — no subscription variants)","operationId":"create_payment_link_from_plan_payment_razorpay_plans_create_payment_link_post","requestBody":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/PlanBasedPaymentRequest"}}},"required":true},"responses":{"201":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/PlanBasedPaymentResponse"}}}},"404":{"description":"Plan Not Found"},"400":{"description":"Bad Request"},"500":{"description":"Internal Server Error"},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/audio-diagnostics/sessions":{"get":{"tags":["Audio Diagnostics"],"summary":"List Sessions","description":"List recent audio diagnostic sessions (both live and from DB).","operationId":"list_sessions_audio_diagnostics_sessions_get","parameters":[{"name":"status","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string"},{"type":"null"}],"description":"Filter by status: streaming, completed, failed","title":"Status"},"description":"Filter by status: streaming, completed, failed"},{"name":"limit","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"integer","maximum":100,"minimum":1,"default":20,"title":"Limit"}},{"name":"offse